articles.title: Trump’s Gaza proposal strikes fear in his new Arab American supporters - The Washington Post
articles.description: Whether Trump can keep these new supporters could have significant implications on key upcoming statewide races, but also on the fragile coalition the party assembled to gain new ground.
articles.content:
